    "causal_summary": "Phase 010 implements pt-03 RQ-A4 (coco few-shot exemplars) + RQ-B2 (memory LLM-curated context packaging) as one L3 packet bundling two presentation-layer features. Both default-off + shadow-first + Phase-005 lift gate. Coco exemplars in SEPARATE response group from new SQLite/vec0 table (capped + TTL + reconciliation); memory data.curatedContext as post-retrieval packaging plan with strict JSON schema validation. Budget split adds retrievalCandidateLimit + presentationLimit + curationTokenBudget knobs. LLM cache extended with mode='context_curation' keying. Hard timeout + deterministic fallback for curator. Stage 4 ordering immutability binding (ADR-004). Soft deps on Phase 007 (better trigger candidates → better curator input), Phase 008 Consumer A (signal quality for example-bank capture), Phase 005 (eval lift gate).",
